wndmenu
=======================================================
wndmenu is an efficient application menu for Windows.

Requirements
------------
In order to build wndmenu you need Visual Studio Build Tools 2022.

Installation
------------------
Open x64 Native Tools Command Prompt for VS 2022.

Afterwards, enter the following command to build and install wndmenu:

    nmake clean install

wndmenu is installed into %LOCALAPPDATA%\wndmenu and registered in 
HKCU\...\App Paths.

Configuration
-------------
The configuration of wndmenu is done by editing config.hpp and (re)compiling the
source code.